@startuml
title Multiplexed Streams over a Single TCP Connection

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

package "Client" {
  [Stream 1\nRequest / Response]
  [Stream 2\nRequest / Response]
}

component "TCP Connection" as TCP

package "Server" {
  [Stream 1\nRequest / Response]
  [Stream 2\nRequest / Response]
}

[Stream 1\nRequest / Response] --> TCP : Frames (S1)
[Stream 2\nRequest / Response] --> TCP : Frames (S2)

TCP --> [Stream 1\nRequest / Response] : Frames (S1)
TCP --> [Stream 2\nRequest / Response] : Frames (S2)

note right of TCP
  Single TCP connection
  carries frames from
  multiple independent streams
end note

@enduml
